  lines:
  - name: Yves
    text: "Don’t worry, Tala. I.. I have a feeling that we can still bring back Damon."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
  - name: Tala
    text: "That’s.. Impossible, Yves. The only thing that you can do is defeat him. He's gone."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
  - name: Tala
    text: "In order to defeat him, you have to get the final source code from the Library. Then, you’ll inject it into the quantum computer on the Penthouse."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
  - name: Tala
    text: "And hopefully– go back to our original timeline."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
